    - **Layer 2:**

        - A green rectangular block is placed on top of the green rectangular block from Layer 1 on the left side.
        - A green rectangular block is placed on top of the green rectangular block from Layer 1 on the right side.
    - **Layer 3:**
        - Two yellow tall rectangular blocks are placed on top of the yellow half-circle blocks from Layer 2, side-by-side.
